sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant M as Main
    participant C as SimulationConfig
    participant N as Network
    participant S as Simulation

    Note over M: Inicio del programa

    M->>M: parseArgs(args)
    M->>C: new SimulationConfig(args)
    C-->>M: config

    Note over M,C: Configuración lista

    M->>N: new Network(config.topology)
    N-->>M: network

    Note over M,N: Red inicializada según topología

    M->>S: new Simulation(network, config)
    S-->>M: simulation

    Note over S: Instancia lista para ejecutar
